    public class SingleColumnAggregatorRecipeImpl
extends AlphaRecipeImpl
implements SingleColumnAggregatorRecipe
    An implementation of the model object 'Single Column Aggregator Recipe'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Delete Rederive Evaluation
    • Optional Monotonicity Info
    • Multiset Aggregation Operator
    • Aggregable Index
    • Group By Mask
